Joy

joy_graph_df <- convo_w_bing %>% filter(nrc_sentiment=='joy') %>% group_by(name,episode_number,nrc_sentiment) %>% tally()

ggplot(joy_graph_df,aes(episode_number,n,color=name)) +
  geom_point()+
  geom_smooth(method='lm')
